Revision history for Sub::Spec::GetArgs::GetPost

0.06     2012-01-20

         No functional changes. Mark deprecation.


0.05     2011-11-23

         No functional changes. Replace Data::Sah::Util with Data::Sah.


0.04     2011-08-31

         No functional changes. Updated because _parse_schema() is moved from
         Sub::Spec::Utils to Data::Sah::Util.


0.03     2011-08-02

         No functional changes. Fixed test script which uses 'YAML' intead of
         'YAML::Syck'.


0.02     2011-07-27

         [ENHANCEMENTS]

         - Plack::Request object ('req') is also accepted as alternative to PSGI
           env ('psgi_env').


0.01     2011-07-26

         First release, extracted from Sub::Spec::HTTP::Server.
